{
  "stem": "5740.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after all, there wasn't a, a, a [INAUDIBLE] job where I was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe I done wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I, I thought, I'm young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if I'm meant to survive, I'll survive here, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if not, so what's the difference where I survive?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few weeks later came a letter from my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she writes, angel of life must have pushed you because all those people who stayed in the orphanage were stripped naked and barefoot and put in a bus.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for many years I didn't know what happened to that bus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You remember the film [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to see the film [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Do you remember-- I don't have to explain here what is the film [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I suppose everybody knows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In that film, I saw the bus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember seeing the bus?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was supposed to be in the bus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All the people who were in that bus, by the time they reached their destination, which was Chelmno, they were all dead because they, they, the pipe with the gas--",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The exhaust was, was taken, was taken into the, the compartment where the people were, and they all arrived dead.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I should have been dead 53 years ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] In the camp I was getting letters from my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was getting parcels from my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- bread, a piece of honey cake.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She used then to send me [NON-ENGLISH], you know, like little parcels daily.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes a piece of bread in it, and sometime with a piece of bread and some money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A [NON-ENGLISH] is like [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] they wanted-- you know, if, if somebody has a business and wants to show his merchandise--",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
